<div class="container--base gray">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        {{!-- Map toggle --}}
        <ul class="map-toggle">
          <li>
            <a href="#collapseMap" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseMap" class="toggle-show">
              Map <span class="material-icons">keyboard_arrow_down</span>
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
        {{!-- Map --}}
        <div class="collapse-wrapper">
          <div class="collapse in" id="collapseMap">
            <div class="map-wrapper">
              <div id="map"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        {{#eq type "MAPD"}}
          {{> PL-results PL.MAPD }}
        {{/eq}}
        {{#eq type "PDP"}}
          {{> PL-results PL.PDP }}
        {{/eq}}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card match-height">
          <div class="card-header display-flex v-center margin-small">
            <div>
              <img src="/images/icon-svgs/mail.svg" alt="Mail" class="img-medium" style="padding-right: 10px;" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="h4 margin-none">Preferred Mail Service Pharmacy</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <p>
              Get savings and convenience delivered right to your mailbox when
              you use home delivery through OptumRX, your plan's preffered mail
              service pharmacy. You could pay less for the same medications.
            </p>
            <p class="margin-none bold">Contact Optum Rx</p>
            <p class="margin-small">
              OptumRx Preferred Mail Service Pharmacy PO Box 2975 <br>
              Shawnee Mission, KS <br>
              66201-1375 <br>
              Call toll-free: 1-877-266-4832, 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. TTY users, call 711.
            </p>
            <a href="#">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card match-height">
          <div class="card-header display-flex v-center margin-small">
            <div>
              <img src="/images/icon-svgs/pharmacy.svg" alt="Pharmacy" class="img-medium" style="padding-right: 10px;" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="h4 margin-none">
                {{#eq type "MAPD"}}
                  Pharmacy Saver offers prescriptions as low as $XX.XX
                {{/eq}}
                {{#eq type "PDP"}}
                  Preferred Retail Pharmacy Network
                {{/eq}}
              </h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            {{#eq type "MAPD"}}
              <p>
                Pharmacy SaverTM is a cost savings prescription drug program
                available to you as a plan member. UnitedHealthcareÂ® has worked
                with many of our network pharmacies to offer even lower prices
                on many common prescription drugs. You may be able to pay less
                than your plan co-pay for your prescription drugs with the Pharmacy
                Saver program.
              </p>
              <a href="#">Learn More</a>
            {{/eq}}
            {{#eq type "PDP"}}
              <p>
                The Preferred Retail Pharmacy Network may help you save money on
                your prescription co-pays. UnitedHealthcare has worked with many
                retail pharmacies to help you get the savings you've been looking
                for. You could save &lt;XX%&gt; or more on co-pays when you fill your
                prescriptions at a preferred retail pharmacy.
              </p>
              <p>
                Savings of &lt;XX%&gt; or more apply to Tier 1 and Tier 2 co-pays on
                the AARP MedicareRx Preferred (PDP) and AARP MedicareRx
                Saver Plus (PDP) plans at a preferred retail pharmacy compared
                with the co-pays of standard pharmacies within the network.
              </p>
              <a href="/drug-cost-estimator-update.html">Estimate your drug costs</a>
            {{/eq}}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="loading-block"></div>
</div>
